<span>For SumoSuggest.com.</span> 
<p>Your privacy is critically important to us. At SumoSuggest.com we have adapted the privacy policy from Wordpress that follow a few fundamental principles:</p>

<p><strong>We don’t ask you for personal information unless we truly need it. (We can’t stand services that ask you for things like your gender or income level for no apparent reason.)</strong></p>
